data.description: Assumable loan at 2.875% available! Fall in love with this Old Town charmer featuring an incredible detached studio and large lot in the heart of it all. This property is beaming with character, offering wonderful indoor and outdoor living. Adorable bungalow style home that flows effortlessly to the outdoor oasis and finished studio, perfect for work-from-home, entertaining a crowd, and more. Other features include space for RV parking, alley access, and fully fenced yard. Zoning allows for the addition of another outbuilding on the lot. Primary short term rental allowed. Located a quick walk from downtown shops/restaurants and popular Lee Martinez park, this one of a kind home offers endless possibilities!
